# Summary
This documentation page explains how to integrate Amplitude cohorts with Twitter Ads to create targeted audiences, including prerequisites (standard Twitter Ads access), setup steps in Amplitude, required user identifiers (Device ID, Email, Handle, X ID, Phone Number), and the cohort export process with notes on Twitter's processing time and privacy practices.

